lead_paragraph: England scored an ignominious double on Monday, becoming the first country to be dumped out of Europe twice in a week and in the process losing both its prime minister and national soccer team manager.

headline.print_headline: Soccer Fans Mock as England Dumped Out of Europe Twice in a Week
